      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4030 - Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) was asked about a man who has dirhams or wealth owed to him by another man, and he invites him to his meal or gives him a gift.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm.\""
        ]
